name: 69 Mizuki Love
description:
69 Mizuki Love - Play an exciting puzzle game with Mizuki. Your weirdo girl waiting you! Collect all the pieces of the puzzle and open the reward. Relaxing music and meditative gameplay will allow to have a good rest after work.

Features


  • 16 levels
  • Relaxing music
  • Meditative gameplay
  • 16 Achievements
  • Your weirdo girl waiting you!
